description: “Where there is food for four, there is food for five"- HoneyIn honor of Honey and the love she had for feeding friends & family her delicious authentic feasts, her son is taking this truck through the streets of the DMV, and in the same warm spirit, serving the locals a “Little Taste of Puerto Rico” in the form of sweet & savory empanadas. Everything from this family-run truck is made with locally grown, raised, and milled ingredients, and you can taste the excellence in every bite. The savory empanadas are filled with tender and perfectly seasoned meats, and each are served with a side of amazingly tasty Arroz con Gandules. The dessert empanadas are filled with your choice of apples, caramel, and cinnamon, or strawberries & mascarpone, and are a perfectly sweet way to wrap up this heavenly hand held meal. For traditional food made that’s with so much care and quality, be sure to head your way to Honey’s Empanadas truck.
name: Honey's Empanadas
